There will be a 3 hour water disruption at The Rest Eco Estate and Curro School on Tuesday, 16 May 2017, from 13:00 until 16:00.Due to new development upgrades at The Rest Eco Estate, it is required to relocate the existing bulk water-pipeline infrastructure in order to accommodate the new development.If you have any queries, please call Sembcorp Silulumanzi on 013 752 6839 or 086 174 5858 (after hours).